 tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pox1665702792737.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pox1665702792737.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pox1665702792737.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pox1665702792737\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Resource Browser (Write Script)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"pox1665702792737__resource_browserwrite_script__21513\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Copy and paste code snippets into the Script Editor.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pox1665702792737__p_d5306e1_d5307e1_d5308e1\">Uniface provides the default\n\t\tlibraries for HTML and ProcScript:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pox1665702792737__li_d2369e1_d2370e1_d2371e1\">UHTML_COMMON—HTML snippets for server page layouts</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pox1665702792737__li_d2372e1_d2373e1_d2374e1\">USCRIPT_COMMON—common Script snippets</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pox1665702792737__li_d2375e1_d2376e1_d2377e1\">USCRIPT_API—trigger snippets for application shells</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pox1665702792737__li_d2378e1_d2379e1_d2380e1\">USCRIPT_<var class=\"keyword varname\">CPT</var>—trigger snippets for specific component types</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"pox1665702792737__note_w3398ab1b5b7_w3399ab1b5_w3400ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> USYSLIBSNP is the template for snippet libraries.\n      </div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pox1665702792737__topic_d2807e1_d2808e1_d2809e1_d2810e1_d2811e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d270040e77\">\n                        How to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pox1665702792737__li_d2381e1_d2382e1_d2383e1\">To select a snippet library, click\n\t\t\t <code class=\"ph codeph\">libsnp</code> in the U-Bar of the Resource Browser, and select the library you want to\n\t\t\t use.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pox1665702792737__li_d2384e1_d2385e1_d2386e1\">To insert a snippet, select a snippet and right-click in either the\n\t\t\t Resource Browser or the code editor and use the menu to insert or copy and\n\t\t\t paste snippets in the desired location.<p class=\"p\" id=\"pox1665702792737__p_d5312e1_d5313e1_d5314e1\">If you select and copy multiple snippets,\n\t\t\t their content is pasted with a line feed separating the different snippets.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pox1665702792737__li_d2387e1_d2388e1_d2389e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hpl1704450799621.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hpl1704450799621.html\" title=\"You can find and insert snippets using the Snippet tab of the Resource Browser in the Write Script worksheet.\">Find and Insert Snippets</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530998\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530998\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Resource Browser (Write Script) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Resource Browser (Write Script) Copy and paste code snippets into the Script Editor. Uniface provides the default libraries for HTML and ProcScript: UHTML_COMMON—HTML snippets for server page layouts USCRIPT_COMMON—common Script snippets USCRIPT_API—trigger snippets for application shells USCRIPT_ CPT —trigger snippets for specific component types Note: USYSLIBSNP is the template for snippet libraries. How to To select a snippet library, click libsnp in the U-Bar of the Resource Browser, and select the library you want to use. To insert a snippet, select a snippet and right-click in either the Resource Browser or the code editor and use the menu to insert or copy and paste snippets in the desired location. If you select and copy multiple snippets, their content is pasted with a line feed separating the different snippets. Find and Insert Snippets Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}